19 “SECTION 6. (1) As used in this section:
20 “(a) ‘Long term care facility’ has the meaning given that term in
21 ORS 442.015.
22 “(b) ‘Residential care facility’ has the meaning given that term in
23 ORS 443.400.
24 “(2) Notwithstanding ORS 441.060 and any rules adopted pursuant
25 to ORS 441.060, a long term care facility or a residential care facility
26 is not required to submit for review plans and specifications for al-
27 terations to an existing facility if the alterations consist solely of al-
28 terations required to replace light fixtures designed to use fluorescent
29 lamps that are subject to the prohibition described in ORS 459.485 with
30 an alternative style of light fixture.
